{"title":"扯破阎锡山“画像”","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":4,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯破阎锡山“画像”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太原城东是大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汾河往西还是山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太原城好像个锅底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤孤摆在汾河滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎锡山、自已讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“太原形势像人样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东山好比太原头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手是南北飞机场；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石咀子和凤阁梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比眼睛高又亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两脚伸在汾河西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太原市内像五脏”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎贼自己画的像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已被扯破多半张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两手干脆被断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两条胳膊受伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两只眼睛早剜掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑袋已离开肩膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮架在头顶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹打到内五脏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎匪饥饿又恐慌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚皮瞠开五脏完！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（转载“人民子弟兵”）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}